HOUSE RESOLUTION NO. 182
BY REPRESENTATIVE MELERINE
COMMENDATIONS: Commends Louisiana State University at Shreveport on its
contributions to the state of Louisiana
1 A RESOLUTION
2 To commend Louisiana State University at Shreveport on its contributions to the state of
3 Louisiana.
4 WHEREAS, Louisiana State University at Shreveport (LSUS) is an integral part of
5 the Louisiana State University System, providing high-quality, accessible, and affordable
6 education to students across northwest Louisiana and beyond; and
7 WHEREAS, LSUS continues to be one of the fastest-growing universities in
8 Louisiana, growing one hundred thirty-three percent over the past ten years, placing it in the
9 top one percent of colleges and universities in the United States for growth in the past
10 decade; the university has achieved record enrollment five semesters in a row; and
11 WHEREAS, LSUS crossed the ten thousand student threshold in the Spring of 2024
12 for the first time in the university's history and surpassed the record in the Fall of 2025 with
13 enrollment reaching the eleven thousand student mark; and
14 WHEREAS, LSUS continues to grow in every enrollment category, including
15 undergraduate, graduate, face-to-face, online, and dual-enrollment; and
16 WHEREAS, LSUS continues to develop new programs that are meeting student
17 interests as well as current workforce needs in the community and throughout Louisiana; and
18 WHEREAS, LSUS graduates more students annually than every other Louisiana
19 university except for the main campus of LSU, and the university leads the state in the
20 number of graduate degrees awarded each year; and
